exim -d -bh 10.0.0.0
mail from:<a@b>
rcpt to:<c@d>
rcpt to:<c@d>
quit
****
exim -d -bh 10.10.10.10
mail from:<a@b>
rcpt to:<c@d>
rcpt to:<c@d>
quit
